parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel pump failure can cause the engine to stall or shut down, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially on highways.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Fuel system leaks can cause fuel to spill onto the ground, creating a fire hazard and increasing the risk of accidents.
